displayName: Jinami, the City of Martial Arts - Pizuma Arena Reception

parameters:
Receptionist: Welcome to the arena. How may I assist you
today?
Receptionist: Who would like to challenge?
Receptionist: Please choose the difficulty level.

Receptionist: We will proceed with the following lineup. Is
that acceptable?
Clea: Well then, here I go.
Thief Nora: I'll cheer you on! Good luck!
Mage Relm: Of course, victory is guaranteed if it's me!
Priestess Sophia: I will prepare to heal.
Thief Nora: I-I'll do my best!
Clea: We'll be cheering for you, so do your best!

Priestess Sophia: A drink before the match... This should
help me fight with confidence!
Mage Relm: Please don't drink before the match!
Clea: Everyone, let's do our best aiming for victory!
Thief Nora, Mage Relm, Priestess Sophia: Yes!
Receptionist: We look forward to your next challenge.

Clea: Thanks to everyone's support, I was able to win the
championship.
Thief Nora: As expected of Clea-san! You're amazing!
Mage Relm: Hehe! It's only natural for such a result!
Priestess Sophia: Oh my, you seem so happy.
Thief Nora: I did it! I won the championship!
Clea: Congratulations, it was a wonderful match, I think.

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, I was able to win the championship.
I'll have a celebratory drink!
Mage Relm: Haa~ You're always drinking, aren't you?

Clea: Thanks to everyone's support, I was able to win the
championship.
Thief Nora: It's okay! Let's try again!
Mage Relm: I can't believe I lost...
Priestess Sophia: Oh my, there are times like this too.
Clea: It's okay, let's try again.

Priestess Sophia: Oh my... I wonder if we ran out of
alcohol?
Mage Relm: Sigh, it's okay to drink now.
Clea: Let's definitely win next time.

Pizuma Arena Manager: Welcome to the Pizuma Arena, where
heart, skill, and body compete!

Clea: I want to participate in the martial arts
tournament.

Pizuma Arena Manager: You're the fourth group, right?
Um... Is this girl your attendant?

Mage Relm: How rude! I am a mage from the academy, you
know!

Pizuma Arena Manager: I apologize for my rudeness! Please
defeat all the rivals in the city of Jinami.

Pizuma Arena Manager: Since the martial arts tournament is
a battle against beasts, there is only one group that is
eligible in the first place.

Pizuma Arena Manager: The notoriety of this tournament has
spread... cough! In order to liven things up, the
preliminaries will be held within the city.
Clea: Understood. Should I come back here once it's over?

Pizuma Arena Manager: That's wonderful confidence! I'm
looking forward to everyone coming back.

Pizuma Arena Manager: I look forward to your return as the
winner.

Pizuma Arena Manager: Have you all survived? Please let me
know when you're ready for battle.

Pizuma Arena Manager: Have you prepared yourself properly?
The opponent is a ferocious beast, so defeat could lead to
death...
Pizuma Arena Manager: Understood, let me guide you!

Pizuma Arena Manager: Welcome to the Pizuma Arena, where
heart, skill, and body compete!

Manager of the Pizma Arena: It was a splendid battle, and
the discerning audience was captivated.

Guard Drone: I am Drone. I have been waiting for a skilled
individual like you to appear.

Clea: If you have a request, please go to the Adventurer's
Guild.

Guard Drone: Adventurer's Guild...! Actually, I have
submitted a request to Oros.

Guard Drone: I apologize for stopping you. It would be a
great help if you could consider my request.

Pizuma Arena Manager: Both of you had a splendid battle! I
never expected General Atu to participate as well!

General Atu: While watching their battle, my body moved to
the arena without my permission!

Pizuma Arena Manager: Clea-sama, please accept the Crown
of the Stalwart King as a symbol of your victory.

Pizuma Arena Manager: Personally, please accept this as a
token of appreciation for your splendid battle.

Pizuma Arena Manager: We are always seeking warriors, and
Pizuma Arena awaits you!
General Atu: What are you talking about?

Clea: General Atu was more terrifying than any beast, as he
held back.

General Atu: Hahaha, just understanding that makes you a
capable person.

General Atu: If the day comes when I can truly battle with
all of you... I won't have to endure boredom anymore.
Clea (If I were to fight... I can't imagine winning...)

Jinami Guard: It seems there is an illegal arena... Even if
you find it, make sure you never get close!

Jinami Guard: It seems there is a scout for an illegal
arena. No matter what kind of profitable offer, you must
never get involved in it.

Nobleman: As expected, the arena is the best! The only
place where blood boils and excitement fills the air outside
of the battlefield!

Wealthy Woman: I'm troubled by my husband being a fan of
the arena... I just want to relax in the villa area of
Vald.

A heavily wounded gladiator: 'Ah, it hurts... It would be
better for your own sake not to participate with half-
hearted determination, you know?'

A magician with a skilled arm: 'It's inefficient to clash
weapons when victory can be achieved by defeating the
opponent.'

Lightly dressed man: There's no point if I don't hit, I'll
prove it in the arena.
Excited man: Today's match was amazing!

Excited Man: The excitement of a thrilling battle! Before
me stands a beautiful woman like a goddess! This is the
best!
Excited Man: Let me share the excitement with you!
Excited man: I'm looking forward to the next match!

Novice Swordsman Otto: Are you really planning to
participate in the individual battles here, where the
strongest warriors from the empire have gathered...?
Clea: Did you feel anything when you watched the battle?

Novice swordsman Auto: I can't put it into words, but I
felt something different from just being confident. I like
battles.

Novice swordsman Auto: I think it's the strength that comes
after overcoming something, probably the strength that I
need to aim for...

Novice swordsman Auto: I want to become stronger by facing
my own weakness that I've been avoiding!

Clea: Even for a coward like me, if you can do it, you
should definitely be able to overcome it.

Clea: Please do your best. As a fellow coward, I'll be
cheering for you.

Novice swordsman Auto: Yes, I will definitely become
stronger!
Clea: What's the matter all of a sudden?

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, Clea-chan, you're such a sinful
girl.
Novice Swordsman Auto: Everyone, you've come!

Clea: Your appearance is completely different. I'm relieved
to see that you've safely advanced.

Mercenary Captain Gale: It seems like you've changed
completely, continuously winning battles. It was truly a
good decision to request the Dragon Slayer!

Mercenary Captain Gale: You can't call yourself a novice
anymore! Take a look, I even got new armor to celebrate your
victory!

Novice Swordsman Auto: Hahaha, Gale-san, you're too
eager...

Novice Swordsman Auto: If I win today, I will become the
champion of the special individual tournament. I really want
Clea-san to see me in that state.

Clea: Understood. I will support you from the spectator
seats.

Novice Swordsman Auto: Thank you very much! I have
preparations to make, so I will return to the waiting room.
Clea: So, what is the request?

Mercenary Captain Gale: As expected, there's someone who's
aiming for the Dragon Slayer, Auto.

Mercenary Captain Gale: It seems that there is someone who
wants to make Auto lose no matter what, as the match result
is a subject of gambling for the nobles.
Clea: Is the request about escorting Auto?

Mercenary Captain Gale: Haha, it seems like a typical
adventurer's guild. We mercenaries always take the
initiative and crush our opponents in advance, so I want
them to be dealt with beforehand.

Mercenary Captain Gale: The opponents are almost completely
identified. They are a group of assassins hired by the
nobles, known as the 'Crushers'.
Clea: Understood, I will head there immediately.

Mercenary Captain Gale: I apologize for being presumptuous,
but I want you to come back in time for Auto's match.

Mercenary Captain Gale: This is not a request, just the
meddling of an old man.
Clea: Understood, I will do my best.

Mercenary Captain Gale: The assassins are a group hired by
the Oros nobles. Be sure not to let your guard down.
